%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e9620f8c34305754d8cc9a7e49e852d9, type: 3}
  m_Name: Rect_En
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  m_LocaleId:
    m_Code: en
  m_SharedData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 17c86a4d3eaf70c4181904b920f70479, type: 2}
  m_Metadata:
    m_Items: []
  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 981162033152
    m_Localized: Exit
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5503791955981
    m_Localized: Dominic highlights the dangers of increased smuggling and piracy
      and suggests allocating resources for urgent repairs and modernization of ships
      in order to quickly return the fleet to protecting the coast.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14482952716017664
    m_Localized: New game
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14482952770543616
    m_Localized: Settings
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5503787761664
    m_Localized: Amalia suggests directing resources to rebuilding the best-preserved
      schools so that children can return to normal education.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5503787761665
    m_Localized: Amalia is concerned about the catastrophic state of hospitals and
      believes it is necessary to urgently purchase medicines, new equipment and
      increase salaries for medical workers.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5503787761666
    m_Localized: "Amalia warns of outbreaks of long-forgotten diseases, calling for
      the country to be urgently supplied with new batches of vaccines to protect
      the most vulnerable citizens \u2013 children and the elderly."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5503791955968
    m_Localized: Amalia points to serious problems with universities, proposing to
      restore buildings and improve working conditions for professors so that young
      people can receive a quality education and stop leaving for abroad.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5503791955969
    m_Localized: Amalia is concerned about overcrowded kindergartens, a shortage
      of teachers and broken equipment, and believes that urgent funds are needed
      to improve conditions for children and teachers.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5503791955970
    m_Localized: Amalia is sounding the alarm over the acute shortage of qualified
      nurses and is proposing to raise their salaries and improve working conditions
      to stop the mass exodus of staff abroad.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5503791955971
    m_Localized: Bianca warns that the oil rigs have stopped and suggests that production
      be restored immediately to avoid losing important clients.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5503791955972
    m_Localized: Bianca is concerned about the production line at the main engineering
      plant stopping and recommends urgent repairs to the equipment to avoid serious
      production delays.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5503791955973
    m_Localized: Bianca reports that the orange processing plant is overloaded and
      advises that additional juice extraction lines be installed quickly to prevent
      crop loss.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5503791955974
    m_Localized: Bianca reports a major leak at the LNG terminal and suggests converting
      some of the infrastructure to a more modern and reliable cryogenic system.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5503791955975
    m_Localized: Bianca points out a critical breakdown of the rolling mill at the
      steel mill and suggests purchasing durable German equipment so as not to disrupt
      the fulfillment of important military orders.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5503791955976
    m_Localized: Bianca is concerned about the state of raw material storage at the
      cement plant and believes it is necessary to invest in the construction of
      new silos and the installation of drying equipment to ensure the stability
      of construction work throughout the country.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5503791955977
    m_Localized: Dominic is concerned about the rise in juvenile crime and suggests
      forming a people's police force to bring order to the streets.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5503791955978
    m_Localized: Domenic believes that there is an urgent need to restore the border,
      strengthening patrols and checkpoints to protect against looters and an uncontrolled
      flow of refugees.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5503791955979
    m_Localized: Dominic warns that military equipment has become unusable and calls
      for immediate resources to be directed towards repairs and spare parts to maintain
      control of the region.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5503791955980
    m_Localized: Domenica insists on the restoration and expansion of the video surveillance
      system in order to promptly prevent crimes and stabilize the situation in the
      city.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5503791955982
    m_Localized: Dominic is concerned that damaged runways and helipads are preventing
      aviation from responding quickly to emergencies and suggests that airfield
      infrastructure be immediately restored.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5503791955983
    m_Localized: Vito suggests building cell towers to enable employees to work remotely.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5503791955984
    m_Localized: Vito proposes to finance the restoration and expansion of railroads
      in order to improve food supplies and prevent an economic crisis.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5503791955985
    m_Localized: Vito recommends allocating funds for the rapid construction of modular
      housing to help affected families and return people to normal life and work.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5503791955986
    m_Localized: Vito proposes to restore the irrigation system to save the crop
      and ensure food security for the region.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5503791955987
    m_Localized: Vito believes it is necessary to purchase agricultural machinery
      and fertilizers to support farmers and help agriculture get back on its feet
      after the destruction.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5503791955988
    m_Localized: Vito advises organizing fairs and temporary markets in the surviving
      areas of the city to help entrepreneurs recover and provide residents with
      necessary goods.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14527393461088351
    m_Localized: President's Advice #1
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14527393461088352
    m_Localized: President's Advice #2
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14527393461088356
    m_Localized: Wow, boss, you're especially generous today!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14527393461088357
    m_Localized: 'Eh, I wish I could add a zero here to the total... '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14527393461088358
    m_Localized: Oh, boss, you can't cook porridge with me...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24356271637573634
    m_Localized: Amalia went out and the door slammed.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24356271637573633
    m_Localized: Dominic walked out and the door slammed.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24356271637573632
    m_Localized: Vito went out and the door slammed.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14527393461088362
    m_Localized: Excellent! With this kind of money we will do everything in the
      best possible way!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14527393461088363
    m_Localized: It's not enough, of course, but we can handle it!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14527393461088364
    m_Localized: This is a big mistake, Boss.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185797
    m_Localized: Oil
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185798
    m_Localized: Factory
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185799
    m_Localized: Oranges
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185800
    m_Localized: LNG
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185801
    m_Localized: Steel
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185802
    m_Localized: Cement
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185809
    m_Localized: Cell towers
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185810
    m_Localized: Railway
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185811
    m_Localized: Housing
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185812
    m_Localized: Farm
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185813
    m_Localized: Agriculture
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185814
    m_Localized: Fairs and markets
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185821
    m_Localized: Bianca found a good contractor to restore the oil rigs.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185822
    m_Localized: Bianca quickly signed a contract with a reliable company from Turin.
      Within a week, the workshops were operating at full capacity, and the workshop's
      productivity increased.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185823
    m_Localized: Bianca installed new lines in a matter of days, managed to save
      most of the harvest. Juice production increased, and foreign partners lined
      up.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185824
    m_Localized: Bianca hired cryo-specialists from the north, everything was fixed
      in record time. The leak was fixed, the pressure stabilized, and the Japanese
      sent a thank-you fax and extended the contract.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185825
    m_Localized: 'Bianca squeezed the maximum out of the budget: she brought in the
      machines, set up the lines, and the rolling went smoothly, like clockwork.
      The plant started working, the schedules were caught up, the profits grew.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185826
    m_Localized: Bianca did not let us down - new silos appeared at the plant, installation
      was carried out around the clock. Raw materials are now stored in ideal conditions,
      and production volumes have increased.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185833
    m_Localized: Vito was purchasing telecommunications equipment
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185834
    m_Localized: Vito entered into contracts for the repair of railway tracks and
      the purchase of new carriages.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185835
    m_Localized: Vito was actively involved in purchasing and installing quality
      modular homes for affected families.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185836
    m_Localized: Vito organized prompt repairs of canals and purchased equipment
      for irrigation systems.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185837
    m_Localized: Vito was actively involved in purchasing and installing quality
      modular homes for affected families.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185838
    m_Localized: Vito was involved in organizing temporary trading platforms and
      negotiating preferential rent for small traders.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185845
    m_Localized: Bianca didn't touch the rigs and moved all the money offshore. The
      barrels remained empty and the buyers were angry.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185846
    m_Localized: The money went to a "paper" modernization. Bianca got involved with
      a dubious contractor who disappeared after the advance payment. The plant stopped
      completely, the workers are on strike, the schedules are disrupted.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185847
    m_Localized: Bianca didn't buy the equipment, but wrote off the funds for non-existent
      "cooling units". The oranges rotted right in the warehouse. The reputation
      is tarnished, contracts with the southerners are broken.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185848
    m_Localized: "Bianca made an agreement with a fictitious company, \u201CArktika
      Gas Tech,\u201D which disappeared immediately after the transfer. The tank
      burst three days later. The losses are huge, the export is disrupted, and Asian
      partners are preparing lawsuits."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185849
    m_Localized: Bianca contacted resellers, paid an advance, and was left with empty
      boxes. Production came to a complete standstill, contracts were broken, and
      only the echo of discontent could be heard in the workshops.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185850
    m_Localized: Bianca secretly sent the allocated funds to an underground supply
      network for the "labor front." The warehouse never appeared, the cement became
      damp, and construction stopped.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185857
    m_Localized: Vito was spotted in an old weapons warehouse.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185858
    m_Localized: Vito secretly sold building materials on the black market to local
      dealers.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185859
    m_Localized: Vito was caught buying cheap, low-quality materials and pocketing
      the money he saved.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185860
    m_Localized: Vito purchased equipment at inflated prices from his cousin, splitting
      the profits with him.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185861
    m_Localized: Vito was seen negotiating the resale of purchased equipment to foreign
      speculators.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185862
    m_Localized: Vito was caught charging personal "commissions" from businessmen
      for prime spots at fairs.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185869
    m_Localized: Chief, all the oil rigs have stopped, buyers of our black gold are
      sounding the alarm, we need to fix the situation urgently.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185870
    m_Localized: Chief, the conveyor at our main machine-building plant has stopped
      again! The transmission shafts are cracking like old bones. If we don't fix
      it, we'll lose three weeks of production!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185871
    m_Localized: Commander, there is trouble with orange processing! The plant is
      overloaded, part of the harvest has already started to spoil. We can install
      additional juice extraction lines - quickly, efficiently and with minimal losses
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185872
    m_Localized: 'Chief, we have problems at the liquefied natural gas terminal.
      One of the tanks has a leak - the pressure is dropping, volumes are not delivered,
      and the Japanese are already calling! There is a solution: transfer part of
      the infrastructure to a new cryogenic system. Not cheap, but reliable.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185873
    m_Localized: Chief, the rolling mill at the steel mill is standing still. The
      bearings are out of order, and we need sheet steel like air right now - especially
      for military contracts. I have equipment in mind from Germany, not new, but
      strong. We need to invest and bring it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259937185874
    m_Localized: Commander, the warehouses at the cement plant are bursting at the
      seams - raw materials are stored in the open air, half of them are already
      damp. If we don't invest in normal silos and drying units, we will lose the
      pace of construction throughout the country.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24356271637573635
    m_Localized: Bianca left and the door slammed shut.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259941380097
    m_Localized: Boss, after the earthquake, most of the office buildings were destroyed.
      Maybe we should allocate funds for cell towers, let's transfer employees to
      remote work?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259941380098
    m_Localized: 'Boss, the situation is difficult: ports and roads are badly damaged,
      food is rotting in warehouses. What if we invest in repairing and expanding
      the railway? That way we can save supplies and keep the economy from collapsing!'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259941380099
    m_Localized: "Boss, hundreds of families have been left homeless after the earthquake.
      I propose that the budget be directed towards the rapid construction of modular
      homes. This way, people will feel safe again and return to work \u2013 the
      economy will start to revive!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259941380100
    m_Localized: Our farmers are desperate, boss! Irrigation canals are destroyed,
      crops are at risk. Maybe we can finance the restoration of the irrigation system?
      We'll save the crop, feed the people and support the economy!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259941380101
    m_Localized: After the earthquake, many farmers were left without machinery and
      equipment. Boss, maybe we should use the money to buy agricultural machinery
      and fertilizers? We'll restore agriculture - people will thank us, and the
      market will come back to life!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14528259941380102
    m_Localized: The city is almost completely destroyed, Boss! Let's organize fairs
      and temporary markets in the surviving areas? Let's support local entrepreneurs
      and help ordinary people buy the most necessary things!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24347940856442880
    m_Localized: Schools
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24347940885803008
    m_Localized: Hospitals
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24347940885803009
    m_Localized: Diseases
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24347940885803010
    m_Localized: Universities
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24347940885803011
    m_Localized: Kindergartens
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24347940885803012
    m_Localized: Nurses
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24347940885803013
    m_Localized: Amalia supervised contractors for the restoration of central school
      buildings.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24347940885803014
    m_Localized: Amalia personally ensured that new equipment and medicines were
      delivered to each hospital and that doctors received the promised bonuses.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24347940885803015
    m_Localized: Amalia organized a large-scale vaccination campaign; the vaccines
      turned out to be high-quality and safe, and the incidence rate rapidly declined.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24347940885803016
    m_Localized: Amalia organized a thorough restoration of the university buildings,
      purchased new teaching equipment, and negotiated the return of the best professors
      back to the country.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24347940885803017
    m_Localized: Amalia successfully opened several new kindergartens, carried out
      high-quality repairs to existing buildings and achieved a significant increase
      in salaries for teachers.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24347940885803018
    m_Localized: Amalia organized a training and professional development program
      for nurses, improved living conditions, and achieved significant salary increases.
      Medical personnel returned to hospitals.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24347940885803019
    m_Localized: Amalia housed the teaching staff and students in tents and transferred
      the remaining money offshore.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24347940885803020
    m_Localized: Amalia bought decommissioned devices at an inflated price, the medicines
      turned out to be expired, and the doctors received only promises. The rest
      ended up in the pockets of her relatives.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24347940885803021
    m_Localized: Amalia bought cheap vaccines of dubious quality, part of the population
      fell ill from the side effects, and the remaining money quietly settled in
      the accounts of her old friend from abroad.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24347940885803022
    m_Localized: Amalia only carried out cosmetic repairs to a couple of classrooms,
      purchased outdated and decommissioned equipment, and spent most of the money
      on building a luxurious villa for her nephew.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24347940885803023
    m_Localized: Amalia only slightly painted the facades, bought the cheapest toys,
      and instead of raising salaries, she threw a lavish party for her grandchildren
      with the remaining money.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24347940885803024
    m_Localized: "Amalia opened only nominal courses without teachers, bought cheap
      uniforms and passed them off as \u201Cstaff support,\u201D and sent the remaining
      money to the accounts of people she knew in a neighboring country."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24347940885803025
    m_Localized: Our schools are destroyed, capoccia. Children have nowhere to study
      and gain new knowledge. I propose to restore and renovate the most surviving
      schools.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24347940885803026
    m_Localized: Oh, dear capoccia, our hospitals have fallen into disrepair. Patients
      lie right in the corridors, there is a catastrophic shortage of medicines,
      and doctors can barely stand on their feet from fatigue! I propose that we
      urgently purchase new equipment and medicines and raise doctors' salaries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24347940885803027
    m_Localized: Oh, my dear capoccia, what a disaster! Outbreaks of diseases have
      become more frequent in the country, which I had forgotten about since my youth!
      Children and old people are defenseless against these viruses, and we have
      very few vaccines, we need new purchases.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24347940885803028
    m_Localized: Oh, my dear capoccia, it hurts my heart to see how our youth strives
      to study, and the universities are almost destroyed! Professors flee abroad,
      classrooms leak, students cannot receive a decent education.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24347940885803029
    m_Localized: Oh, capoccia, the kids are completely unsupervised! Our kindergartens
      are overcrowded, there aren't enough beds, toys are broken, and the teachers
      are running away, unable to handle the workload
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24347940889997312
    m_Localized: Oh, capoccia, we have almost no qualified nurses left in our country!
      Girls work day and night, and many are already leaving for abroad - the conditions
      are better there and the salaries are higher.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24347940889997313
    m_Localized: My dear, thank you for your generosity, now we can definitely cope!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24347940889997314
    m_Localized: This is very little for our needs, my dear...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24347940889997315
    m_Localized: "Oh, my dear, you shouldn\u2019t have done that\u2026"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24355636267626496
    m_Localized: Crime
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24355636296986624
    m_Localized: Border
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24355636296986625
    m_Localized: Tanks
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24355636296986626
    m_Localized: Crime
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24355636296986627
    m_Localized: Fleet
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24355636296986628
    m_Localized: Aviation
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24355636296986629
    m_Localized: Dominic was involved in selecting and recruiting trusted people
      for police raids.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24355636296986630
    m_Localized: Dominic personally led the defense and successfully prevented the
      looters from entering, maintaining order on the approaches to the city.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24355636296986631
    m_Localized: Dominic quickly organized repairs and restored key vehicles, allowing
      the army to quickly respond to threats and ensure the safety of residents.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24355636296986632
    m_Localized: Dominic personally supervised the installation and operation of
      the cameras. The increased surveillance allowed several crimes to be quickly
      solved and the situation to be stabilized.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24355636296986633
    m_Localized: Dominic successfully organized the rebuilding of the fleet. The
      warships quickly returned to patrol and stopped several smuggling attempts.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24355636296986634
    m_Localized: Dominic oversaw the repair work and was able to quickly return the
      aircraft to service, ensuring a rapid response and saving many lives.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24355636296986635
    m_Localized: Dominic secretly made purchases of firearms for his people.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24355636296986636
    m_Localized: Dominic used some of the funds to strengthen his own influence and
      increase his personal security, leaving the borders vulnerable.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24355636296986637
    m_Localized: Under the guise of repairing military equipment, Dominic secretly
      resold some of the parts on the black market, thereby weakening the army's
      combat readiness and putting the city at risk.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24355636296986638
    m_Localized: Under the guise of expanding video surveillance, Dominic installed
      hidden cameras to personally spy on government officials and political rivals,
      diverting resources from general security.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24355636296986639
    m_Localized: Dominic used part of the funds to secretly sell ships and weapons
      to private contractors, significantly weakening the coastal defenses.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24355636296986640
    m_Localized: Under the guise of aircraft repairs, Dominic secretly leased some
      of the equipment to private companies, leaving the army without the necessary
      air force in a critical situation.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24355636296986641
    m_Localized: After the disaster, teenage gangs roamed the streets. We need free
      hands to rein them in. It's high time to organize people's police units.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24355636296986642
    m_Localized: Our border is destroyed. If we don't strengthen patrols and restore
      checkpoints, marauders and refugees will soon flock here. I propose that we
      immediately establish a defense system and checkpoints.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24355636296986643
    m_Localized: The disaster has disabled most of our military equipment. Without
      its prompt restoration, we risk completely losing control over the region.
      We urgently need to allocate resources for repairs and purchasing spare parts.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24355636296986644
    m_Localized: In order to respond quickly to threats and nip crime in the bud,
      we need to restore and expand the video surveillance network. The sooner we
      get the eyes of the city back, the safer the situation will be
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24355636296986645
    m_Localized: Without immediate repairs to the ships and strengthening of the
      fleet, we risk encountering smuggling and piracy. I request that resources
      be allocated for urgent modernization and return of the warships to duty
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24355636296986646
    m_Localized: After the earthquake, our aviation is practically paralyzed. Without
      urgent repair of runways and restoration of helipads, we will lose the ability
      to quickly respond to emergency situations.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24355636296986647
    m_Localized: The country will be proud of you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24355636296986648
    m_Localized: This is extremely insufficient for the request of law enforcement
      agencies.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24355636296986649
    m_Localized: You will regret it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  references:
    version: 2
    RefIds: []
